12:[["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-4 text-muted-foreground leading-7","children":"Performance is a feature. Here are a few changes that tend to move the needle."}],"\n",["$","h2",null,{"className":"mt-8 text-2xl font-bold text-foreground","children":"1. Optimize Images"}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-4 text-muted-foreground leading-7","children":["Use the right format (WebP/AVIF when supported) and size. Next.js ",["$","code",null,{"className":"rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm","children":"Image"}]," does a lot of this for you: lazy loading, responsive ",["$","code",null,{"className":"rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm","children":"srcset"}],", and placeholders."]}],"\n",["$","h2",null,{"className":"mt-8 text-2xl font-bold text-foreground","children":"2. Reduce JavaScript"}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-4 text-muted-foreground leading-7","children":"Ship less JS. Prefer server components so that only interactive parts load on the client. Code-split routes and heavy libraries."}],"\n",["$","h2",null,{"className":"mt-8 text-2xl font-bold text-foreground","children":"3. Cache Wisely"}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-4 text-muted-foreground leading-7","children":["Set cache headers for static assets. Use ",["$","code",null,{"className":"rounded bg-muted px-1.5 py-0.5 font-mono text-sm","children":"stale-while-revalidate"}]," for data that can be a bit stale. For static sites, SSG gives you a fast first load."]}],"\n",["$","h2",null,{"className":"mt-8 text-2xl font-bold text-foreground","children":"4. Measure"}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-4 text-muted-foreground leading-7","children":"Use Core Web Vitals (LCP, FID, CLS) and real-user metrics. Optimize what you measure; otherwise you're guessing."}],"\n",["$","p",null,{"className":"mt-4 text-muted-foreground leading-7","children":"Start with one of these and measure again."}]]
